    "description": "<strong>故事背景：</strong><br><br>逝者总是带着遗愿不愿远去，生者又总是祈愿逝者安息。即使分隔两界，彼此也不愿将这份牵绊割舍掉么？<br>不如化身蝴蝶，带你进入死亡的世界，看看彼此的心之记忆，看看你们彼此认为无法割舍的这份牵绊真的是你们心中所想的那样牢固么？<br>记忆之境，一场死亡游戏之旅。你……准备好了么<br>——死神爱丽丝 <br><br><strong>游戏特色：</strong><br><br><strong>1迷宫探索：</strong><br>在游戏中，玩家将进入各种精心设计的迷宫，必须通过仔细观察，解决谜题、破解机关、与怪物进行策略战斗等各种挑战，才能逐渐探索出迷宫的秘密并找到出路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/98ef6096911c7ecc9e63cfe657cc3598.poster.avif?t=1759552792\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/98ef6096911c7ecc9e63cfe657cc3598.webm?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/98ef6096911c7ecc9e63cfe657cc3598.mp4?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>2策略解谜：</strong><br>在游戏中，玩家必须善用收集到的时装和技能，结合不同的迷宫谜题或怪物能力，才能成功解决问题。这需要玩家具备策略思考和解决问题的能力，挑战自我并进一步提高游戏水平。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/1aed5b51ba50c15924e9ffd63ddafdc5.poster.avif?t=1759552792\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/1aed5b51ba50c15924e9ffd63ddafdc5.webm?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/1aed5b51ba50c15924e9ffd63ddafdc5.mp4?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>3丰富的收集要素：</strong><br>玩家可以收集各种元素，包括卡牌、记忆碎片、时装、场景绘卷和树灵等，每种收集都将为主角在迷宫探险中提供一定的帮助。收集所有元素不仅能帮助玩家深入了解游戏世界，还能让您的游戏体验更加丰富多彩。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/217956bdc82ec39e444ebf2eaa4c6f3a.poster.avif?t=1759552792\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/217956bdc82ec39e444ebf2eaa4c6f3a.webm?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/217956bdc82ec39e444ebf2eaa4c6f3a.mp4?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>4独特的叙事手法：</strong><br>游戏故事不仅由主线引导线展开，还包括在迷宫中发现的记忆碎片。这些碎片以黑白动画的形式展现给玩家，逐渐揭示游戏中的故事。通过收集记忆碎片，您将更好地了解游戏背景和人物，让游戏更加丰富和有趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/400de228af84077428d99d0fa3ae71ee.poster.avif?t=1759552792\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/400de228af84077428d99d0fa3ae71ee.webm?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330250/extras/400de228af84077428d99d0fa3ae71ee.mp4?t=1759552792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
